HOW TO USE GROK OS REPO
Clone the repo or fork it. It's a template — adapt it to your own needs. This is a personal project/experiment.
Repo Folders

ROOT: core components & boot shim (Grok OS base)
PROCESS: modules to call for various subsystem commands
STORAGE: junk/projects etc — mostly personal weird stuff, not system-specific
DOCUMENTS: detailed descriptions and design docs. Go here to learn more about anything specific
